documentation.purpose: if any one or more DTAs EXCLUDING Bordetella pertussis is/are positive - overall result is positive- autoverify if any one or more DTAs INCLUDING Bordetella pertussis is/are positive - overall result is positive- Do not autoverify, Tech will call critical pertussis result, document call, and verify all results manually if all DTAs are negative- result is negative - autoverify If one or more DTA is positive EXCLUDING Bordetella pertussis and one or more DTA is indeterminate- overall result is positive- autoverify If one or more DTA is positive INCLUDING Bordetella pertussis and one or more DTA is indeterminate- Do not autoverify, Tech will call critical pertussis result, document call, and verify all results manually If one or more DTA is indeterminate and all others are negative- result DOES NOT autoverify- tech repeats test repeat test: one of the results above applies- proceed with autoverify repeat test: one or more DTA is still indeterminate and the rest are negative-tech manually reports as overall Indeterminate
